&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;进行逆向中序遍历&lt;img data-src=&#34;E:%5Ctypora%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%5Cimage-20220322141449103.png&#34; alt=&#34;image-20220322141449103&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
