&lt;h5 id=&#34;树的存储结构-image-20220322161735312&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#树的存储结构-image-20220322161735312&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 树的存储结构   &lt;img data-src=&#34;E:%5Ctypora%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%5Cimage-20220322161735312.png&#34; alt=&#34;image-20220322161735312&#34;&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;
